title: Static Analysis

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.REQUEST_IGNORE_BATTER.description: Permission an application must hold in order to use

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.READ_LOGS.description: Allows an application to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (co.blocksite.SplashScreenActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.

strings:
"accessibility_hint_description" : "1. Find BlockSite & tap on it
2. Enable BlockSite"

"accessibility_hint_description_samsung_9" : "1. Scroll to Installed Services
2. Click on Installed Services
3. Find BlockSite
4. Enable BlockSite"

"accessibility_hint_description_samsung_9_in_settings" : "1. Scroll & click on Installed Services
2. Find BlockSite
3. Enable BlockSite"
"accessibility_reminder_notification_text" : "BlockSite is off. Enable BlockSite now to start improving your focus and productivity!"

"accessibility_service_description" : "Enable accessibility to allow BlockSite to prevent your browser from entering websites and apps you have chosen to block. By enabling accessibility, you acknowledge that you have read and understand our Privacy Policy."
"activity_about_opt_out_description" : "If you opt out, your data won't be used for anything other than to provide, improve and develop BlockSite products and services"
"add_app_edit_text_helper" : "App must be on your device in order to block"
"add_app_hint_edittext" : "App name (must be installed on your device)"
"add_site_edit_text_label" : "Search for a keyword, site or app"
"add_site_error_message" : "Please type in a valid web address"
"add_site_error_text" : "Please type in a valid web address"
"add_word_warning_body" : "You will block many websites and apps with the keyword "%s""
"add_word_warning_title" : "Are you sure you want to add this keyword?"
"admin_disabled_pooup_text" : "Admin privileges are disabled for BlockSite. Please enable uninstall prevention by allowing BlockSite admin privileges."

"admin_disabled_settings_message" : "Are you sure?
Disabling Admin Privileges for BlockSite means deactivating you will be able to uninstall the app"
"admin_enabled_body" : "BlockSite will now make sure you are free from distractions"
"admin_pooup_text" : "Please enable device administration to prevent BlockSite from being uninstalled. Don’t worry, we don’t use this permission for anything other than this feature."

"battery_optimize_from_notification_pooup_text" : "To ensure you have the best experience on BlockSite, please be aware that users have reported that disabling battery optimization for BlockSite has significantly reduced reoccurring issues due to battery optimization. We advise making sure your battery optimization is turned off."

"battery_optimize_pooup_text" : "Users have reported that disabling battery optimization for BlockSite has enhanced their experience on BlockSite. Turn off this feature below to continue to take even more control of your time."
"blocked_image_setting_subtitle" : "Show images over blocked sites and apps"
